{"tid":2045834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（武漢肺炎）鍾南山：中国患病率、病死率全球最低","createTime":"2020-06-01T04:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T12:13:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e28bd03ebd67a4ee9572526b4c842506208bbd7","tid":2045834,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2020/04/06/20200406000071M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2F20200406000071M.jpg&h=eb784f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國知名抗疫專家鍾南山。（中新社提供）(資料照片/CNA)<br />\n<br />\n陸媒報導，中國抗疫專家鍾南山說，中國對俗稱武漢肺炎的2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)採取「在震中集中圍堵，在震外聯防聯控」的正確策略，「到目前為止，按照10萬平均人口來說，中國的患病率、病死率都是全世界最低的」。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山並稱，中國的疫苗研究進度在世界第一梯隊。「到目前為止，我們已經有5款疫苗在進行二期的臨床試驗，所以我們不會比其他國家落後」。<br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平5月29日在給鍾南山、袁隆平等25名科技工作者代表的回信中指出，創新是引領發展的第一動力，科技是戰勝困難的有力武器。面對突如其來的新冠肺炎疫情，全國科技工作者迎難而上、攻堅克難，在臨床救治、疫苗研發、物質保障、大數據應用等方面夜以繼日攻關，為疫情防控鬥爭提供了科技支撐。<br />\n<br />\n官媒央視新聞31日報導，鍾南山5月30日在談到習近平的回信時說，「大家都備受鼓舞，非常開心。特別習主席談到，創新是引領發展的第一動力，科技是戰勝困難的有力武器，這兩句話給了我們最大的鼓舞」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2066314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2066314&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=1ee310e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2066314</a>"},{"pid":"2486762eda616a7d0ce38164a9c42b70ccbdbae0","tid":2045834,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"其實香港俾美國制裁就係今日香港升市嘅主因<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2045813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2045813</a>"},{"pid":"d06fb64d6f1c06722adae7e45e75d96801bab3bc","tid":2045834,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"識玩一定信中共數據<br />\n<br />\n鍾青山話中国抗疫最強<br />\n<br />\n即係有疫苗唔比外國知<br />\n即係有治療方法唔公開<br />\n（公佈都唔work即係講大話）<br />\n即係故意投毒全世界，所以中國無事<br />\n即係隻菌係人造，專門攻擊非黃種人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條條都死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdeea4b90b63a1a4963510a5d331a06ac3472c73","tid":2045834,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"隱瞞疫情老作病例梗係最低喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e900a02e241148a40d0c0491a0b5fcf7145ca521","tid":2045834,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23be8baa7a29a002f34758ae889351a1180ed97c","tid":2045834,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"高溫療法"}]}